<li>the site of his son, biologist and co-author Gert Jan: <a href="http://www.gertjanhofstede.com" class="external free" title="http://www.gertjanhofstede.com" rel="nofollow">http://www.gertjanhofstede.com</a></li>
<li>The Culture in the Workplace Questionnaire™, Dr. Hofstede's assessment instrument that identifies individual cultural value preferences and analyzes them against country averages: <a href="http://www.itapintl.com/tools/culture-in-the-workplace-questionnaire-cw/itapcwquestionnaire.html" class="external free" title="http://www.itapintl.com/tools/culture-in-the-workplace-questionnaire-cw/itapcwquestionnaire.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.itapintl.com/tools/culture-in-the-workplace-questionnaire-cw/itapcwquestionnaire.html</a></li>
<li>Information on cultural dimensions: <a href="http://stephan.dahl.at/intercultural/Hofstede_dimensions.html" class="external free" title="http://stephan.dahl.at/intercultural/Hofstede_dimensions.html" rel="nofollow">http://stephan.dahl.at/intercultural/Hofstede_dimensions.html</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.kwintessential.co.uk/intercultural/dimensions.html" class="external text" title="http://www.kwintessential.co.uk/intercultural/dimensions.html" rel="nofollow">Hofstede's dimensions simplified</a> by Kwintessential</li>
<li><a href="http://www.clearlycultural.com/geert-hofstede-cultural-dimensions/" class="external text" title="http://www.clearlycultural.com/geert-hofstede-cultural-dimensions/" rel="nofollow">Hofstede's cultural dimensions</a> World maps of Geert Hofstede's 5 cultural dimensions</li>
<li><a href="http://www.kwintessential.co.uk/intercultural-business-communication/tool.php" class="external text" title="http://www.kwintessential.co.uk/intercultural-business-communication/tool.php" rel="nofollow">Intercultural Business Communication</a> Simple application of Hofstede's dimensions into a practical business tool</li>
<li>Geert Hofstede is a member of the Editorial Board of The International Scope Review <a href="http://www.socialcapital-foundation.org/TSCF/TSCF%20journal.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.socialcapital-foundation.org/TSCF/TSCF%20journal.html" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
<li>An article about the impact of Dr. Hofstede's work on business practices: <a href="http://www.itapintl.com/facultyandresources/articlelibrarymain/hofstedes-consequences-the-impact-of-his-work-on-consulting-and-business-practices.html" class="external free" title="http://www.itapintl.com/facultyandresources/articlelibrarymain/hofstedes-consequences-the-impact-of-his-work-on-consulting-and-business-practices.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.itapintl.com/facultyandresources/articlelibrarymain/hofstedes-consequences-the-impact-of-his-work-on-consulting-and-business-practices.html</a></li>
</ul>


